1304.name: L-Ag60Sn
1304.Applications:
Joining: Steels, Cast iron, Copper, Copper alloys, Stainless steel, Nickel and Nickel alloys. Also suitable for dissimilar joints between these metals. 
Do not use this alloy above working temperatures of 200ºC
1304.Suitable_For: Brazing: Steels, Cast iron, Copper, Copper alloys, Stainless steel, Nickel and Nickel alloys. Also suitable for dissimilar joints between these metals.
